data.description: Fantastic 3 bedroom Ranch style home that offers lots of upgrades. The complete interior has been freshly painted, it has a New Roof and New Windows. The kitchen has New cabinets, New Granite Countertops and New Appliances. There is New LVP flooring and New carpets and New lighting and plumbing fixtures throughout. This is just to name a few new features, schedule your showing today to see this beauty.
